    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <h2 class="h3 fw-bold mb-3">Understanding the Crisis</h2>
      <p class="text-muted">Electronic waste contains severe neurotoxins and carcinogens. When dumped in municipal waste streams, substances like lead, mercury, and cadmium leak into soil and contaminate groundwater resources.</p>
      <p class="text-muted">By raising awareness and implementing proper urban mining processes, we can divert these hazards away from vulnerable ecosystems and return valuable materials to the circular economy.</p>
